=== Purchase Information === Product Title: Manicure and Pedicure Nail Clipper from POWERGROOMING - Powerful Trimmer for Thick and Thin Finger Nails and Toe Nails - Included Nail File and"Catcher" for Easy Cleanup (1 Pack) Review Date: 2018/12/15 Store: POWERGROOMING Average Rating: 4.1 Product Details: {'Brand': 'POWERGROOMING', 'Material': 'Stainless Steel', 'Blade Edge': 'Straight', 'Blade Material': 'Stainless Steel', 'Target Audience': 'Women, Men', 'Package Dimensions': '3.8 x 1.3 x 1 inches; 3.21 Ounces', 'UPC': '653233212735', 'Manufacturer': 'POWERGROOMING'} Review Text: I really loved the modern look of these clippers and file; however, i took one star away as the small nail file is not as sharp as I would have liked. I'm used to an old Revlon diamond file that works much faster.
As others have said, you can very easily remove the black base on the nail clippers if it seems unwieldy to you. It felt just fine to me. Review Title: Super attractive clippers and file in a leather look case. Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Aussie Hairspray Instant Freeze Extreme Hold 7 Ounce (207ml) (2 Pack) Review Date: 2020/10/21 Store: Aussie Product Description: ['Aussie Hairspray Instant Freeze Extreme Hold 7 Ounce (207ml) (2 Pack)'] Average Rating: 4.5 Product Details: {'Scent': 'Unscented', 'Liquid Volume': '7 Fluid Ounces', 'Item Form': 'Oil', 'Brand': 'Aussie', 'Number of Items': '2', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Product Dimensions': '4.3 x 2 x 8.5 inches; 11.04 Ounces', 'UPC': '381519078040 787734409902 038785520000', 'Manufacturer': 'Aussie'} Review Text: A tiny spritz of this not only holds my hair, but makes it look fuller.
I imagine it will last a long time; so, its also a great value.
I was always loath to try these freeze-type hairsprays, thinking they would look stiff, but this doesn’t.
No discernible fragrance, either. Review Title: Exactly what I’ve been looking for. Fantastic hold with no residue or helmet head. Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: COLORGRAM Artist Formula Auto Brow Pencil 0.25g- True Beauty K-Drama Makeup, Built-in-Spoolie, Clump-Free Formula, Softly Glides, Natural Look (01 Ash Brown) Review Date: 2021/06/19 Store: COLORGRAM Product Description: ["Featuring a unique, triangular tip, Brow Definer's retractable pencil design is ideal for outlining and filling your brows in one fluid motion. The custom spooley end is created with a precise width and firmness to seamlessly blend color."] Average Rating: 3.8 Product Details: {'Brand': 'COLORGRAM', 'Item Form': 'Pencil', 'Finish Type': 'Natural', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Product Benefits': 'Softening', 'Product Dimensions': '0.59 x 0.71 x 4.53 inches; 3.7 Ounces'} Review Text: This was pretty impossible to use. It was so dry and hard that it wouldn’t even apply color to my brow. I
I would strongly suggest going with the Maybelline brow precise or the Maybelline brow ultra slim. Both of those are phenomenal and fairly priced. I think you can get them with Amazon’s subscribe and save, too. Review Title: I could barely get this to apply to my brow…old product? Rating: 1.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Ivnil hair removal spray pack of 2 Review Date: 2021/08/18 Store: Ivnil Average Rating: 3.8 Product Details: {'Item Form': 'Spray', 'Recommended Uses For Product': 'Anti-aging', 'Skin Type': 'Sensitive', 'Brand': 'Ivnil', 'Unit Count': '1.00 Fl Oz', 'Package Dimensions': '2.76 x 2.32 x 2.28 inches; 5.61 Ounces', 'UPC': '752771042412'} Review Text: I have been using this eye cream for months, day and night, and just adore it. It’s very emollient without being greasy at all.

I am usually sensitive to products and this gave me no negative reactions.

It only takes a tiny little bit to moisturize my upper and lower lids. Of course, I stay away from the eyelash area as I don’t want any of this in my eyes.

One jar has lasted for months.

The only thing I don’t like is the container as it means sticking my finger into it and I really don’t like that delivery system. I would vastly prefer if it had a small nozzle tube that could stand on its end. I know it wouldn’t look as fancy, but it would be far more user friendly. Review Title: I have been using it for months and love it! Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Badgley Mischka 1.7floz/50mL Body Lotion Toiletries for Bathroom, Guests, Hotels, Motels, and Lodging (30 pack) Review Date: 2021/08/22 Store: HOTEL EMPORIUM, INC. Average Rating: 5.0 Product Details: {'Brand': 'HOTEL EMPORIUM, INC.', 'Item Form': 'Lotion', 'Unit Count': '1.00 Count', 'Number of Items': '30', 'Item Volume': '1.7 Fluid Ounces', 'Package Dimensions': '9.53 x 6.38 x 3.82 inches; 4.26 Pounds', 'UPC': '653753520143'} Review Text: As they sent me the shampoo, this review is for that.
I think it’s excellent quality and has a super leather. It cleaned my hair beautifully and left it fairly soft, but that was with a rinse out conditioner, too.
I would highly recommend it. Review Title: Review for shampoo, not lotion. Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Gryph & IvyRose Coat of Arms Hydrating Lotion for Kids - Hydrating Moisturizer with Shea Butter & Coconut Oil - All Natural, Sustainable, Cruelty Free, No Parabens, No Sulfates, Vegan - USA Made - 8oz Review Date: 2021/09/15 Store: Gryph & IvyRose Average Rating: 4.4 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Gryph & IvyRose', 'Scent': 'Coconut Shea', 'Item Form': 'Lotion', 'Active Ingredients': 'Sweet Almond Oil', 'Unit Count': '1.00 Count', 'Package Dimensions': '5.67 x 2.28 x 2.24 inches; 8 Ounces', 'UPC': '856991007210'} Review Text: This lotion would get five stars, but I think it’s expensive for what it is and the container is definitely not user-friendly.
If it had been in a tube it would have gotten four stars from me.
The lotion itself is very thick and emollient. It is gentle and has virtually no fragrance.
But getting it out of the plastic bottle with a difficult to use top meant squeezing really hard. More work than I want for a bit of moisturizer. Review Title: Good lotion, expensive, and in a poorly designed container. Rating: 3.0 --------------------------------------------------

SUMMARY:
The individual exhibits a distinct shopping pattern characterized by a preference for aesthetically appealing and functional personal care items, notably skewed towards beauty and grooming products. Ratings indicate a balanced appreciation for quality, with consistent high ratings (4.0-5.0) for effective products, especially in hair care and skin care. Sentiments reveal a tendency to favor items that deliver value and multifunctionality, as seen in the positive feedback on a hair spray that offers hold without stiffness and a moisturizing lotion noted for its gentleness.

Common themes include a notable contrast between expectations and actual performance, particularly in the experiences with eyebrow products and hair removal sprays—indicating a dislike for underperforming, difficult-to-use products. Additionally, price sensitivity emerges, as critiques often mention high prices or a preference for better value alternatives, suggesting that product price points are crucial in the decision-making process.

Quality preferences lean towards cruelty-free and natural formulations, indicating a conscious choice for brands that reflect ethical values. User experience is paramount, especially concerning product design and packaging, where frustrations about usability impact overall satisfaction. This person's core preferences center on effective, visually appealing products, with an emphasis on value, quality, and handy designs.

target_interaction.title: Great pencil, but the Gray-brown color was too dark for me.
target_interaction.text:
I really like this pencil, but the color, gray brown, was too dark for me and I couldn't use it. As there was no other color that would be better, I can't buy this product; however, if you can find a good color for you the quality and ease of application is wonderful.
I also recommend that they stamp the name of the company on the actual pencil so that if I ever wanted to buy it again I would know how to do that. Right now, the pencil that has no writing, only the color number 04 at the bottom.
